</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="12.[212,321,1066,1090]" box="[212,321,1066,1090]" pageId="12" pageNumber="2151">
<emphasis box="[212,321,1066,1090]" italics="true" pageId="12" pageNumber="2151">Diagnosis</emphasis>
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="12.[212,1171,1106,1162]" pageId="12" pageNumber="2151">This species is represented by the fore wing having two large black patches, and the sacculus is about same width and sinuate on dorsal margin.</paragraph>
